ever after, right?

08:29.568 --> 08:31.468
I can live with that.

08:31.570 --> 08:35.974
If it doesn't work out,
you got a place to stay?

08:36.075 --> 08:37.976
I'll find a place.

08:38.077 --> 08:39.409
Tell you what.

08:39.513 --> 08:41.811
I'll wait
in the parking garage.

08:41.914 --> 08:44.406
You score, you call
on the car phone.

08:44.518 --> 08:47.646
You strike out,
I'll get you a hotel.

08:47.754 --> 08:49.779
You're all right, Argyle.

08:49.890 --> 08:53.951
Just remember that
when you sign for the tip.

09:16.884 --> 09:18.112
Hi.

09:18.219 --> 09:19.618
Good evening.

09:19.720 --> 09:22.120
I'm here to see
Holly McClane.

09:22.223 --> 09:24.123
Just type it in there.

09:29.230 --> 09:31.425
Cute toy.

09:31.532 --> 09:34.831
If you have to
take a leak,

09:34.936 --> 09:36.802
it finds
your zipper.

09:51.153 --> 09:52.313
Christ.

09:57.426 --> 09:59.326
30th floor.

09:59.428 --> 10:00.793
The party.

10:00.896 --> 10:03.660
They're the only ones
left in the building.

10:03.765 --> 10:05.164
Take the express elevator...

10:05.267 --> 10:07.168
until you hear the noise.

10:07.269 --> 10:08.669
Thanks.

11:05.429 --> 11:06.828
Champagne, sir?

11:06.932 --> 11:08.331
Yeah, thanks.

11:42.801 --> 11:45.497
Oh, I'm sorry.

11:45.603 --> 11:48.334
Hey, Merry Christmas!

11:51.610 --> 11:53.510
Jesus.

11:53.612 --> 11:56.012
Fuckin' California.

11:57.283 --> 12:00.442
Why don't
I talk to him right now?

12:00.553 --> 12:01.611
Hi.

12:01.721 --> 12:02.949
I'm looking for-

12:03.055 --> 12:04.283
Holly Gennero.

12:04.390 --> 12:05.482
Yeah.

12:05.591 --> 12:07.457
You must be
John McClane.

12:07.561 --> 12:08.960
Joe Takagi.

12:09.062 --> 12:10.962
How was your ride in?

12:11.064 --> 12:12.964
I have you to thank?

12:13.066 --> 12:15.466
Seemed the least
we could do.

12:15.569 --> 12:17.969
Quite a place
you have here.

12:18.071 --> 12:19.470
It will be.

12:19.573 --> 12:20.972
Several floors are
under construction.

12:21.074 --> 12:23.474
Holly went to fax
some documents.

12:23.577 --> 12:24.976
In the meanwhile,

12:25.078 --> 12:26.978
her office is
right back here.

12:28.949 --> 12:31.213
<i>Ellis.</i>

12:31.318 --> 12:35.085
I was just making a call.

12:35.188 --> 12:38.852
I want you to meet
John McClane,

12:38.960 --> 12:40.325
Holly's husband-

12:40.428 --> 12:41.656
Holly's policeman.

12:41.763 --> 12:44.493
Ellis is in charge of
international development.

12:44.599 --> 12:47.500
Heard a heck of a lot
about you.

12:47.602 --> 12:49.536
Missed some.

12:50.938 --> 12:52.838
Can I get you anything?

12:52.940 --> 12:54.339
Food? Cake?

12:54.442 --> 12:56.342
Some watered-down
champagne?

12:56.444 --> 12:58.503
No, thank you.
I'm fine.

12:58.612 --> 13:00.946
You throw quite a party.

13:01.048 --> 13:02.447
I didn't realize...

13:02.549 --> 13:04.780
they celebrated
Christmas in Japan.

13:04.886 --> 13:06.787
Pearl Harbor
didn't work out,

13:06.889 --> 13:10.950
so we got you
with tape decks.

13:11.060 --> 13:14.291
Actually, it's sort of
a double celebration.

13:14.396 --> 13:18.093
Holly helped us close
a big deal today.

13:18.200 --> 13:21.465
<i>I'll be out in
a couple of minutes.</i>

13:25.007 --> 13:26.975
John.

13:29.978 --> 13:32.469
Have you met everyone?

13:32.581 --> 13:34.981
We've been
sticking him with spears.

13:35.085 --> 13:36.985
Of course, he has.

13:37.087 --> 13:39.487
She was made
for the business.

13:39.589 --> 13:40.988
Tough as nails.

13:41.091 --> 13:42.490
I was hoping...

13:42.592 --> 13:43.991
you made that flight.

13:44.094 --> 13:45.994
Show him the watch.

13:46.096 --> 13:47.154
Later.

13:47.263 --> 13:48.662
Go on.
Show him.

13:48.765 --> 13:50.130
What, are you
embarrassed?

13:50.233 --> 13:53.293
<i>A token of appreciation
for her hard work.</i>

13:53.403 --> 13:54.995
It's a Rolex.

13:55.105 --> 13:57.505
I'm sure
I'll see it later.

13:57.607 --> 14:00.735
Is there a place
where I could wash up?

14:00.844 --> 14:03.278
Sure.

14:18.628 --> 14:19.993
Ellis gets very depressed...

14:20.096 --> 14:21.655
this time of year.

14:21.765 --> 14:24.632
He thought he was
God's greatest gift.

14:24.735 --> 14:26.635
Yeah.
I know the type.

14:26.737 --> 14:30.138
Think he's got
his eye on you.

14:30.241 --> 14:31.640
That's okay...

14:31.742 --> 14:33.141
I have my eye...

14:33.244 --> 14:34.644
on his private bathroom.

14:34.745 --> 14:36.144
Where you staying?

14:36.247 --> 14:38.148
Things happened so fast,

14:38.250 --> 14:41.151
I didn't get
a chance to ask you.

14:41.253 --> 14:43.983
Cappy Roberts
retired out here.

14:44.089 --> 14:46.819
He told me
I could bunk with him.

14:46.925 --> 14:49.655
Cappy retired, huh?
Where's he live?

14:49.761 --> 14:50.921
Ramona.

14:51.029 --> 14:53.122
Pomona.

14:53.231 --> 14:54.323
Huh?

14:54.432 --> 14:55.490
<i>Pomona.</i>

14:55.600 --> 14:56.794
Pomona.

14:56.902 --> 14:58.836
Yeah.

14:58.937 --> 15:01.770
You'll be in the car
half the time.

15:01.873 --> 15:03.272
Why don't we make it easy?

15:03.375 --> 15:05.936
I have a spare bedroom.

15:06.044 --> 15:08.741
It's not huge
or anything, but...

15:08.848 --> 15:12.249
the kids would love
to have you at the house.

15:12.351 --> 15:14.444
They would, huh?

15:17.557 --> 15:19.286
I would, too.

15:22.061 --> 15:23.119
Ooh!

15:23.229 --> 15:25.163
Sorry.

15:31.571 --> 15:33.471
I missed you.

15:41.048 --> 15:43.278
I guess you didn't
miss my name, though, huh?

15:43.383 --> 15:47.319
