- I know exactly...

16:14.215 --> 16:16.581
what your idea
of our marriage should be.

16:16.684 --> 16:18.447
Ms. Gennero, I-

16:20.221 --> 16:21.882
Excuse me.

16:21.990 --> 16:23.753
Hi.

16:23.858 --> 16:27.191
Um, Mr. Takagi
is looking for you.

16:27.295 --> 16:30.628
<i>He wants you
to say something to the troops.</i>

16:34.569 --> 16:36.162
Speech time.

16:36.272 --> 16:38.672
Be back in
a few minutes.

16:50.585 --> 16:52.485
That was great,John.

16:52.588 --> 16:53.987
Good job.

16:54.089 --> 16:55.647
Very mature.

17:45.409 --> 17:47.309
So Kareem rebounds, right?

17:47.411 --> 17:49.311
Feeds Worthy on the break,

17:49.413 --> 17:51.745
over to A.C., to Magic,
then back to Worthy, right?

17:53.184 --> 17:54.310
Boom!

