mister-

02:05:18.481 --> 02:05:20.745
Ellis' murder,
for one thing,

02:05:20.850 --> 02:05:22.113
<i>property damage,</i>

02:05:22.219 --> 02:05:24.619
<i>interfering with
police business.</i>

02:06:03.661 --> 02:06:06.596
<i>All right!
