incredible ordeal,

02:06:35.694 --> 02:06:37.719
what are
your feelings?

02:06:41.700 --> 02:06:44.726
Well, well, well.

02:06:44.837 --> 02:06:46.737
Merry Christmas,
Argyle.

02:06:46.839 --> 02:06:48.067
Merry Christmas.

02:06:51.010 --> 02:06:53.240
